  "texts": [
    "However, it is important to note that these datasets have limitations and biases that must be taken into account when using them for research.",
    "IoT applications using DL methods in bioand medical informaticsIoT applications employing DL methods in bio-and medical informatics constitute a transformative frontier in healthcare technology.",
    "These applications leverage the interconnectedness of devices and sensors within the IoT ecosystem to revolutionize patient care, diagnosis, and treatment.",
    "DL algorithms, renowned for their prowess in processing vast and complex data, are employed to analyze diverse biomedical data streams, including physiological measurements, medical imagery, and genomic information.",
    "This enables real-time monitoring of patient health, early detection of anomalies, and personalized treatment plans."
